@bmoharrisbank // @adidashockey

node.text:
Won the Raffl. ✅

We have signed Michael Raffl to a 1-year contract through the 2021-22 season.

node.text:
Hawk, yeah! Welcome to #TexasHockey, Jani Hakanpaa. 🌟
 
We have signed Jani Hakanpaa to a 3-year contract through the 2023-24 season.

node.text:
56 forever 🌟

We're proud to announce Sergei Zubov's number will be raised to the rafters during the 2021-22 season.
